                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "heightened",
                "level": 4,
                "text": "Your battle form is Large, and your attacks have 10-foot reach. You instead gain 15 temporary HP, attack modifier +16, damage bonus +6, and Athletics +16."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
